---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import SiteHeader from '../components/SiteHeader.astro';
---


<Layout
  title="How to Order | Fastlane Synthetics"
  description="How to order AMSOIL products through Fastlane Synthetics."
>
  <main class="min-h-screen bg-white text-slate-900">
   <SiteHeader currentPath="/how-to-order" />

    <section class="relative overflow-hidden bg-slate-900">
  <div class="absolute inset-0">
    <img src="/AMSOIL-background1.png"
      alt="Truck on mountain road"
      class="h-full w-full object-cover object-center opacity-75"
    />
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-slate-950/55"></div>
  </div>

  <div class="relative z-10 mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 py-16 md:px-10 md:py-20">
    <div class="max-w-4xl">
      <p class="text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.24em] text-cyan-300">
        How to Order
      </p>

      <h1 class="mt-4 text-4xl font-black leading-tight text-white md:text-6xl">
        A simple path to finding and ordering the right AMSOIL products.
      </h1>

      <p class="mt-6 max-w-3xl text-lg leading-8 text-slate-200">
        Fastlane Synthetics helps you identify the right AMSOIL products for your vehicle,
        motorcycle, equipment, or small fleet. Orders are completed directly through AMSOIL.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

    <section class="bg-slate-50">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 py-16 md:px-10">
        <div class="grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-2">
          <div class="rounded-3xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-8 shadow-lg transition-shadow duration-300 hover:shadow-xl">
            <p class="text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.24em] text-[#005baa]">
              Step 1
            </p>
            <h2 class="mt-3 text-2xl font-black text-slate-900">
              Tell us what you use
            </h2>
            <p class="mt-4 leading-8 text-slate-600">
              Share your year, make, model, engine, equipment type, or general application so the right AMSOIL options can be narrowed down quickly.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="rounded-3xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-8 shadow-lg transition-shadow duration-300 hover:shadow-xl">
            <p class="text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.24em] text-[#005baa]">
              Step 2
            </p>
            <h2 class="mt-3 text-2xl font-black text-slate-900">
              Get a product recommendation
            </h2>
            <p class="mt-4 leading-8 text-slate-600">
              We help point you toward the AMSOIL products that best fit your vehicle, equipment, and intended use.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="rounded-3xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-8 shadow-lg transition-shadow duration-300 hover:shadow-xl">
            <p class="text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.24em] text-[#005baa]">
              Step 3
            </p>
            <h2 class="mt-3 text-2xl font-black text-slate-900">
              Order directly through AMSOIL
            </h2>
            <p class="mt-4 leading-8 text-slate-600">
              Once you are ready, you complete your purchase directly through AMSOIL using dealership-linked ordering paths.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="rounded-3xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-8 shadow-lg transition-shadow duration-300 hover:shadow-xl">
            <p class="text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.24em] text-[#005baa]">
              Step 4
            </p>
            <h2 class="mt-3 text-2xl font-black text-slate-900">
              Come back anytime for help
            </h2>
            <p class="mt-4 leading-8 text-slate-600">
              If you are unsure what to buy next time, need help with another vehicle, or want guidance on a different application, support is available.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="bg-white">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 py-16 md:px-10">
        <div class="grid gap-10 rounded-3xl border border-slate-200 bg-slate-50 p-8 shadow-sm md:grid-cols-[1.1fr_0.9fr] md:p-12">
          <div>
            <p class="text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.24em] text-[#005baa]">
              Important Note
            </p>
            <h2 class="mt-4 text-3xl font-black leading-tight text-slate-900 md:text-5xl">
              Pricing and checkout are handled through AMSOIL
            </h2>
            <p class="mt-5 text-lg leading-8 text-slate-600">
              This website does not display AMSOIL product pricing. Product pricing, account options, and checkout are handled directly through AMSOIL.
            </p>

            <div class="mt-8 flex flex-col gap-4 sm:flex-row">
              <a
                href="/contact"
                class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-[#005baa] px-8 py-4 text-base font-bold text-white transition hover:bg-[#004a8c]"
              >
                Ask for Product Help
              </a>

              <a
                href="https://www.amsoil.com/offers/pc/?zo=5039461"
                target="_blank"
                rel="noopener noreferrer"
                class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-[#ef1c25] px-8 py-4 text-base font-bold text-white transition hover:bg-[#004a8c]"
              >
                Save Up to 25%
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="rounded-2xl bg-white p-6 shadow-sm ring-1 ring-slate-200">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-black text-slate-900">
              Helpful information to have ready
            </h3>

            <ul class="mt-5 space-y-4 text-slate-700">
              <li class="flex gap-3">
                <span class="mt-1 text-[#005baa]">✓</span>
                <span>Vehicle year, make, and model</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex gap-3">
                <span class="mt-1 text-[#005baa]">✓</span>
                <span>Engine or equipment type</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex gap-3">
                <span class="mt-1 text-[#005baa]">✓</span>
                <span>How the vehicle or equipment is used</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex gap-3">
                <span class="mt-1 text-[#005baa]">✓</span>
                <span>Any questions about filters, fluids, or maintenance intervals</span>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="relative overflow-hidden bg-slate-950">
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-slate-950/80"></div>

      <div class="relative mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 py-14 md:px-10 md:py-16">
        <div class="max-w-3xl">
          <p class="mb-4 text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.24em] text-cyan-300">
            Ready When You Are
          </p>
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-black text-white md:text-5xl">
            Need help before you order?
          </h2>
          <p class="mt-5 max-w-2xl text-lg leading-8 text-slate-200">
            Reach out if you want help choosing the right AMSOIL product before ordering through AMSOIL.
          </p>

          <div class="mt-8 flex flex-col gap-4 sm:flex-row">
            <a
              href="/contact"
              class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-[#ef1c25] px-8 py-4 text-base font-bold text-white transition hover:bg-[#d8151d]"
            >
              Contact Us
            </a>

            <a
              href="/about"
              class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-xl border border-white/20 px-8 py-4 text-base font-bold text-white transition hover:bg-white/10"
            >
              Learn About Us
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="bg-[#07142b] text-white">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 py-16 md:px-10">
        <div class="grid gap-10 md:grid-cols-4">
          <div class="md:col-span-2">
            <img
              src="/logo.jpg"
              alt="Fastlane Synthetics logo"
              class="h-16 w-auto object-contain"
            />

            <h3 class="mt-6 text-2xl font-black">
              Ready to upgrade to AMSOIL?
            </h3>

            <p class="mt-4 max-w-xl leading-8 text-slate-300">
              Get practical product guidance and a straightforward path to ordering the right AMSOIL
              products for your vehicle, motorcycle, or equipment.
            </p>

            <div class="mt-6 flex flex-col gap-4 sm:flex-row">
              <a
                href="/how-to-order"
                class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-[#ef1c25] px-6 py-4 text-base font-bold text-white transition hover:bg-[#d8151d]"
              >
                Shop AMSOIL
              </a>

              <a
                href="/contact"
                class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-xl border border-white/20 px-6 py-4 text-base font-bold text-white transition hover:bg-white/10"
              >
                Contact Us
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h4 class="text-lg font-black">Fastlane Synthetics</h4>
            <p class="mt-4 leading-8 text-slate-300">
              Your trusted independent AMSOIL dealer serving customers with clear product guidance
              and support.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <h4 class="text-lg font-black">Quick Links</h4>
            <div class="mt-4 flex flex-col gap-3 text-slate-300">
              <a href="/" class="transition hover:text-white">Home</a>
              <a href="/about" class="transition hover:text-white">About</a>
              <a href="/how-to-order" class="transition hover:text-white">How to Order</a>
              <a href="/articles" class="transition hover:text-white">Articles</a>
              <a href="/contact" class="transition hover:text-white">Contact</a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-12 border-t border-white/10 pt-6 text-sm text-slate-400">
          © 2026 Fastlane Synthetics. Independent AMSOIL Dealer.
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</Layout>